Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:56.91,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,300)}總之就是繞著彎的愛的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間還有叫作天然呆的人種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個朋友甚至問她時間都會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放戀愛進行時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個很有趣喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪  現在幾點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就發生了這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說手上拿著飲料就去看表了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  那樣的蠢貨現實中不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  這個無論夢中還是童話中都沒有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼實驗一下唄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬還真喜歡實驗啊手工啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得好  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  來點喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  現在幾點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  這樣就能證明了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然呆是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣千秋  明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田是特別的笨蛋當不了參考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人家的衣服弄濕還說人家是笨蛋好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  內田你那是什麼打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是冬馬做的緊急用女僕裝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在衣服干之前就穿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有緊急用便裝啊  我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提  尺寸只有小學生的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使喚我的意圖滿滿呢  我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:52.67,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊  實驗成功了一回也不能下結論啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  下回絕對不會這樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來換個人來實驗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿誰來做實驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像內田那樣的可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野好像沒什麼破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用阿珍做實驗好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我說  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香今天是戴了手錶出門的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香應該會把數字那面戴在手腕內側
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內側？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  春香回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試坐在春香的旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女僕  端些水過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香不會上當的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在時間  4點12分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是報時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…馬上就4點13分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  沒在相信春香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二～宮～同～學～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.91,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香現在幾點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3點半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  讓我看看你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手背
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春香  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼春香  一會見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  難道是要去春香學姐家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  春香說要給我們做蛋糕吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃  春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待不周
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希學姐真能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身材那麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那麼小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小裏面的中等左右
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希的手也很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不小  手指很長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就來比比手的大小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說大話  你以為能贏過我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小差不多一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我的手指更纖細更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那麼地纖細啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就是那麼纖細
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美的戒指讓真希戴戴不就清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就比比看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  不去阻止這兩個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下吧  二位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是剛剛聊什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想真希穿不穿的進我家的女僕裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果付錢我會穿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  戒指去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個好像很值錢  沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友的男朋友給買的然後我拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有上幾萬還是沒有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾萬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了戒指握在手裏還當作丟了  弄得大家興師動眾幫我找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼天然呆的事  說不出來太丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要我裝自然而然找到的也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被問「在哪找到的？」就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾到哪裏去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不行了  總之讓它真正不見一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是別人給我的東西  不用那麼介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像幾百塊來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了兩位數  你沒記錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是剛剛聊什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿女僕裝春香就會給錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指在我的包裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過戒指就在這個屋子裏好好找的話會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  在哪找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然解釋不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指在我包裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  該道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然解釋不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟在包裏真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:12:00.04,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  解釋一下她們為什麼一個勁地道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.04,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}恐怖蜜蜂人阿珍！！篇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.08,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}打倒蜜蜂人阿珍！！篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是啊  冬馬給我做了衣服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬還會做針線活啊  有點意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她還挺厲害的  會讓你吃一驚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子要不要也拜託她做一套衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  再說也很難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來夏樹泡澡就很久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要花掉一集電視劇的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬告訴我了哦  說你洗澡很花時間來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是洗澡要花很久的那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一點也不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡不就是簡單地過一下流程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖一下  再擦乾就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬那傢伙居然說些多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來不想讓春香學姐知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不管怎麼說都很難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  夏樹的那個眼神是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂夏樹  有什麼事讓你這麼難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是仁美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我洗澡很花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個很難為情的眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  洗澡時間很久？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那麼難為情的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不管怎麼說  洗澡久是女孩子會做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以男孩子會覺得難為情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣  剛才沒給夏樹台階下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我剛想起還有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼這麼輕易地就把難為情的事告訴我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很直白地就說出來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他就一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你連難為情的部分也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是繞著彎的愛的告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  其實我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說的洗澡的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗的時間長能促進血液循環  還能使人放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能只沖個身子就完事哦  知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  春香學姐這麼說我就照做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹  關於剛才的話題…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:15:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗澡其實…也要很久的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得自己說了很難為情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡時間久是好事情  很能促進血液循環
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還很能讓人放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道這對身體很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你沒有其他正經事要跟我說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼難為情的事情都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼好難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要泡到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視劇都放完一集了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就繼續去看綜藝節目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是那家店的甜甜圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感  那家店的甜甜圈有一半是用幸福做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有一半是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對現在來說重要麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這多出來的一個甜甜圈要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就用猜拳決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你晚出了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有晚出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我再去倒杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續來吃甜甜圈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪散步了  我的甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你有看到我的甜甜圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在讀書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在騷擾千秋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來了  你們兩個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們之中某個人吃掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我們其中一人吃掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒吃到的那個會告狀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就不存在什麼甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就沒有甜甜圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是幻影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這糖霜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證明了甜甜圈確實存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之前吃的甜甜圈上並沒有撒糖霜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管吃得怎麼小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的嘴邊都會沾上一點糖霜的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就讓我來嘗嘗你們的嘴吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  是我們分著吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  坦白地還真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也無所謂了  總之為了確認一下就讓我來嘗嘗味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在吵什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個傢伙把我的甜甜圈吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  多出來的那個甜甜圈是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的份呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我們才沒有在吃甜甜圈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得夏奈的身上有股肉桂的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎  其實我本身就像肉桂一樣啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？夏奈吃的是肉桂味的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了肉桂味的什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了什麼啊…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她們把春香的甜甜圈吃掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是多出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  是我忘了那個是給春香留的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我在減肥  其實也沒關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  反正…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家大女兒心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪夏奈把春香的甜甜圈吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們吃掉的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈沒注意到  是你的不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃掉肉桂味的夏奈的不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二比一  夏奈的不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著別用少數服從多數來決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  少數服從多數就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二比一  就決定是少數服從多數了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都說了別這麼決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須做點什麼  讓大女兒的心情好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真舒服真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身打扮既難為情又不便於行動  能脫掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是商量好了麼  要用打掃衛生來作為吃掉春香姐姐的甜甜圈的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒說要扮成女僕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的獻身精神還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底你就是個在溺愛和隨心所欲環境中長大的小女兒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋也是小女兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天就讓我來把你的本性糾正過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們幫忙打掃衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去做飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說起來夏奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女僕裝穿不上…我的主人…
